While BetterMail uses Google Inc.'s Gmail service it is in no way
associated with Google Inc.  By clicking accept you acknowledge 
that at any time Google may update Gmail or Android in a way that
may render BetterMail unusable.

Since BetterMail makes use of Google Inc.'s Gmail service you must
also agree to Gmail's terms of service.

Privacy Notice:

BetterMail will only use your e-mail address to authenticate with
Gmail and to show on-device notifications.  BetterMail does not
collect any other type of personal information.

Use of BetterMail is subject to Google Inc.'s Gmail privacy policies.

